      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 14 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 14 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：无交害，匪咎，艱則无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the first NINE, undivided, there is no approach to what is injurious, and there is no error. Let there be a realisation of the difficulty (and danger of the position), and there will be no error (to the end).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
