      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 14 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：公用亨于天子，小人弗克。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows us a feudal prince presenting his offerings to the Son of Heaven. A small man would be unequal (to such a duty).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
