      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：匪其彭，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject keeping his great resources under restraint. There will be no error.</seg>
