      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 14 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：厥孚交如，威如；吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows the sincerity of its subject reciprocated by that of all the others (represented in the hexagram). Let him display a proper majesty, and there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
